        <abstract>
            <p>Glad CL plans trip to Amiens to investigate flints and post-glacial period.</p>
            <p>Mentions support by Huxley, Hooker, and Lubbock at Oxford BAAS meeting. Asa Gray also goes on fighting.</p> 
<p>Likes article by William Hopkins ["Physical theories and the phenomena of life", <hi rend="italic">Fraser’s Mag.</hi> 61 (1860): 739–52; 62 (1860): 74–90].</p> 
            <p>Comments on hybrids of hare and rabbit.</p>
        </abstract>
